Runtime dependencies
--------------------

Installing and running the full Hermes integration also installs upstream
IntentFrame packages from PyPI. Those packages are licensed separately:

  - Apache-2.0 SDK packages (examples):
      intentframe-core, intentframe-actor, intentframe-bundle-sdk,
      intentframe-executor-sdk, intentframe-native-kit

  - AGPL-3.0-only runtime packages (examples):
      intentframe-supervisor, intentframe-runtime, intentframe-server

See https://github.com/intentframe/intentframe for upstream licensing details
and commercial licensing options.

